STEPS FOR FIREBASE AUTH INTEGRATION -

1.create a new project in google.firebase.com
2.create a web-app from the firebase project and create a init file in your project with all secret SDK app information
3.export the SDK app. and create a auth pass the app in the auth and export it also.
4.go to firebase authentication settings and select the email and password auth from there.
5.create sign-in and up pages on the project
5.npm install --save react-firebase-hooks install npm package to handle auth